---
// Services Section - Serviços oferecidos
---

<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Header da Seção -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll fade-up">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
        Nossos
        <span class="text-[#00bc61] relative">
          Serviços
          <svg class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3" viewBox="0 0 200 12" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 10C20 5 40 2 60 3C80 4 100 7 120 4C140 1 160 5 180 8C185 9 190 10 198 10" stroke="#00bc61" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" class="animate-pulse"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[#A7A9AC] max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Oferecemos um portfólio completo de serviços digitais para transformar seu negócio e acelerar seu crescimento.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de Serviços -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Serviço 1: Sites & E-commerces -->
      <div class="group p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 hover:border-[#00bc61]/30 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 h-full grid grid-rows-[auto_auto_1fr_auto] gap-4 animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-200">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#00bc61]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#00bc61]/20 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:scale-110">
